PAN AMERICAN WORLD AIRWArS SYSTEM
You can make definite reservations
for over the Holidays
to Bermuda, Mexico, Hawaii,
the west Indies or wherever
you choose
- or you can let the person who receives
the Gift Certificate decide that later.
Without fighting your way through Christmas
shopping crowds ... without even going to a store...
you can order one of the most unusual, most appre-
ciated Christmas presents you have ever given!
A Pan American Gift Certificate, which you can
arrange for by telephoning your Travel Agent or
Pan American, can make the most unforgettable
gift of 1948!
Only Pan American, you know, flies to all 6
Continents-offering you a choice of 61 countries
and colonies. Here are a few of these trips-
MEXICO CITY from Houston
